"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"We are seeing cases of fraud rising. Everybody posting that they get hacked or someone fooled them and emptied all their funds.\\n\\nTake some simple measures to avoid it (if you are using software wallets like metamask) :\\n\\n* Never share your password or seed phrase with ANYONE.\\n* Never share your screen while making YouTube videos and showing your metamask wallet\\n* Never click on links saying “Click here to get 1 Bitcoin”.\\n* Never sign through your wallet without reading the contract.\\n* Many a times your metamask wallet will pop up and say that “fix it”. Which means that it is fake and someone is trying to hack you.\\n* Never type your seed phrase on any devices. Never ever.\\n* Always check the domain name correctly before using any dapp.\\n* Never reveal your wallet address for GIVEAWAYS and telling the world that your wallet address. Work hard and earn. Don’t fall for fake giveaways.\\n\\n  ### Only you are responsible for your funds . Be safe.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/wjVdivUYnx01m_TChNNJ9.png?height=1155&width=3464)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640275908,\"title\":\"Simple cautionary measures\"},\"digest\":\"FgAng8ROFOVSUZQLNG_X3nwXW3WcqMA42_QfuMe2_po\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xaef4842A2C6f44ed2D8C4BFf94451126D79A065E\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2HAoWpy2xkVc7dgZVSBnCZNHqYmqM6Wl9FoN_24qJlw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_MS_uBzoVpeePKESswckMI_3KkheqBl0qOXv5GuMFpo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"WDoatVZeyjeI4CBqSMhSwrYTSgZn1kxAvf6uk0Q2_gzpHToQFkDwNHgAj_kg4uE6njZk25JZlQpVuZgEeRTGDg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe81ffa5fd57d743fadab7d7bbbe6c044b4e5208f7327762da953781bf7c241d53f4d77af45c52396ca79183f91cd280a93e7342ec6c57a9a2a2c1f05416c2eae1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\